Subject: FEATURE: propagate constants into expressions
Date: Mon, 4 Jan 2010 13:28:49 -0700
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

When a variable has no assignments, its initial value can be copied  
into all expressions if the value is fixed.  In this case, simplify  
should be applied to reduce the expressions, if possible.

